title: Corey Taylor Responds To MGK After Slipknot Diss
author: Rock Feed
description:
Slipknot frontman Corey Taylor responded to MGK after the musician called out the band during his Riot Fest set. MGK claimed he refused to let Corey Taylor appear on the album, with Corey Taylor proving that he refused the appearance.
